  "texts": [
    "• The Facebook_Midterm dataset contains Facebook posts collected the same way and spanning the same period as Twitter_Midterm [56].",
    "We extract the data fields of interest from each social media post, including the user ID, post ID, and domain names of the shared links.",
    "If a link is shortened when shared on these platforms, a pre-processing step is performed to extract the domain name from the expanded URL.",
    "Posts with domain names of platforms such as amazon.com, yelp.com, youtube.com, etc. are not considered.",
    "To limit noise, we further retain only accounts sharing at least five links and posts containing domains that are shared at least five times across the dataset."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "• The Facebook_Midterm dataset contains Facebook posts collected the same way and spanning the same period as Twitter_Midterm [56]."
  ]
}